Ricardus
Ricardus is the fusion between Ricardo Fort & Frida Kahlo, each edition can also have a shout out to other iconic celebrities.
After a dark experience, Ricardus is slowly returning to a halfway normal being by merging with Mikey Wilson. At this point we don't know if he changes teams a lot or if he just has the largest t-shirt collection in the metaverse.
besides this you can see clear references in the tats to other artists such as dot pigeon, thr33som3s or singerie apes.
